highlights.text: Dangrangto has the most spots on Viral Songs Vietnam. “một bài hát không vui mấy - Extended Version” is the highest at #22.
“Exit Sign” by HIEUTHUHAI and marzuz has been on Viral Songs Vietnam the longest, at 206 days straight.
“Who are you?” by Saga Faye is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Vietnam at #31.
“Mùa Xuân Đầu Tiên - Live With Orchestra” by Lân Nhã is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Vietnam, up 21 spots at #70.
